{"tid":40225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港府首次承認海洋垃圾湧海灘　源自大陸垃圾船","createTime":"2016-12-15T05:23:23.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T05:56:47.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"063115d042496ccef92f1bbc2c415a054a16d34b","tid":40225,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:23:23.000Z","msg":"《香港01》今年八月找到線索，發現有「垃圾船」在珠海萬山海域(距大嶼山40公里)非法傾倒垃圾，懷疑是本港海洋污染的源頭，特首梁振英稱盡快與內地部門跟進。事隔近半年，港府首次承認年中「攻港」大批海洋垃圾來自內地垃圾船，又引述廣東省環保廳稱已將涉嫌違法船隻和人員扣押，遏止有關問題。海事處亦已加緊巡查香港水域以的漂浮垃圾情況，在過去數月，未有發現大量漂浮垃圾再現的情況。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/312775/xlarge/3dbf5b5a4fe6fc07fa618627bc50152a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F312775%2Fxlarge%2F3dbf5b5a4fe6fc07fa618627bc50152a.jpg&h=21ee018d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有運載過百噸垃圾的船涉嫌倒垃圾早前被扣查，位置是和大嶼山距離僅50公里的珠江口。<br />\n<br />\n環境局局長黃錦星以書面回答議員提問時表示，就懷疑有船隻在珠海萬山群島一帶水域傾倒垃圾一事，環保署聯同漁護署及海事處在今年八月接獲報告後，已旋即與廣東省環保廳和負責漁業及海事的部門跟進。<br />\n<br />\n廣東扣押違法船隻和人員<br />\n<br />\n當局引述廣東省環保廳表示，內地執法單位已開展海上和陸上行動，追查有關非法傾倒垃圾行為，並已加強巡查，嚴厲打擊非法傾倒垃圾。廣東省環保廳告悉行動已初步取得成效，涉嫌違法船隻和人員已經被扣押，而海上違法傾倒垃圾事態得以遏制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hk01.com/media/images/312767/xlarge/d5dae2e644cefdc0a770457171a6ffd5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F312767%2Fxlarge%2Fd5dae2e644cefdc0a770457171a6ffd5.jpg&h=c5736351&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今年中，本港多個海灘出現大量垃圾，特首梁振英率領多名高官到大嶼山海灘清理垃圾。（資料圖片）"},{"pid":"1e0e43fc4042d5c8519b18cd75d7b5164d1486bc","tid":40225,"uid":53406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:39:44.000Z","msg":"感謝黨"},{"pid":"abc3522716109ea82eed2be9e1b2a8d8db2b2d03","tid":40225,"uid":18320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T05:41:36.000Z","msg":"屌你老母留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cecb3ce9b203f848c5bd74f3e9e45df4b343d5dc","tid":40225,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:28:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec8f9ff6444144c7ff00a208da326b469b719c4","tid":40225,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T06:33:11.000Z","msg":"仲洗估？"},{"pid":"9aa86641044d322f7106262ce62565d56f4c7de7","tid":40225,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:12:08.000Z","msg":"叫班愛國廢中食晒堆垃圾佢"},{"pid":"71eec5dc3e09ac86e1891f13898166f7eaab048b","tid":40225,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T07:16:47.000Z","msg":"唔係日本仔黎執垃圾都唔會回應"},{"pid":"8cdb611dff54329ea752261b0fc80e40d7b09749","tid":40225,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:00:13.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 百幾噸垃圾倒落海<br />\n除左支那仲有邊個國家嘅人做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5483206e8b9bc21272bab1d9d461e5c5a1874ecc","tid":40225,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T08:01:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58b0b4b56823035b4ede301403e1eb5e8002868a","tid":40225,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacbf06b73cb3b6dcbee5b996a201c3904d31f01","tid":40225,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T17:09:54.000Z","msg":"夠竟支那送大禮可以有幾多種方式"},{"pid":"ee6ba160f0ed4860d3921ccdeb829352825788ba","tid":40225,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T04:55:16.000Z","msg":"認咗又點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7add37c9b088f388fd14d31aea38cb5dcce5768f","tid":40225,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T05:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1414086906a199fd2616fdea98c0f5d84af